            <p>1828 South Rittenhouse Square<lb/>
                Phila. 17 Sep. 79<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev. S. Morais&#44;<lb/>
                My dear Sir&#44;<lb/></p>
            <p>At a meeting<lb/> of the Board of Adjunta<lb/> held on the sixteenth<lb/> instant it was re&#45;<lb/>solved &#34;That the sum<lb/> of Two Hundred &#38; fifty<lb/> dollars &#40;&#36;250&#45;&#45;&#41; be re&#45;<lb/>imbursed to the Rev. S Morais&#44; in two<lb/> payments of one hun&#45;<lb/>dred &#38; twenty five dollars<lb/> each &#40;&#36;125&#45;&#45;&#41; &#40;payable<lb/> respectively on the<lb/> 15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> of October and 15th<lb/> of January next&#41; as a<lb/> part of the amount<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>of his salary conceded<lb/> by him for the year<lb/> 5639.&#34;¬ù<lb/></p>
            <p>I am further instructed<lb/> by the Board to extend<lb/> to you their congratula&#45;<lb/>tions on the approaching<lb/> holidays in which<lb/> you will believe I<lb/> cordially join<lb/></p>
            <p>&#38; am very sincerely yours<lb/>
                Charles J Cohen<lb/></p>
        </body>
